	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 1, on a person who rises up to discredit the canons of the great council of saints in Nicaea, ፩ ትእዛዝ፡ እመቦ፡ ብእሲ፡ ዘተኃየለ፡ ይሥዐር፡ ዘሠርዑ፡ ማኅበር፡ ዐቢይ፡ ቅዱሳን፡ በኒቂያ፡" ;
