	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 11, Anyone who wants to be one with us and participate in our faith (lit. in his soul in our mystery), the deacon must bring him to the priest or to the bishop, ትእዛዝ፡ ፲፩ ኵሉ፡ ዘአፍቅረ፡ ይደመር፡ ምስሌነ፡ ወይሳተፍ፡ በነፍሱ፡ ውስተ፡ ምሥጢርነ፡ ይደልዎሙ፡ ያምጽኦሙ፡ ዲያቆን፡ ኀበ፡ ቀሲስ፡ አው፡ ኀበ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
