<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.18.12> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 12, If a man has a wife or a woman has a husband, they must teach them to be patient with each other, ትእዛዝ፡ ፲፪ ወለእመ፡ ኮነ፡ ብእሲ፡ ዘቦቱ፡ ብእሲተ፡ አው፡ ብእሲተ፡ እንተ፡ ባቲ፡ ምተ ይምሀርዎሙ፡ ከመ ይትዐገሡ፡ በበይናቲሆሙ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
