<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.18.13> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 13, if a person who is possessed by a demon wants to come to our faith, first they must teach him the fear of God and heal him, ፲፫ ትእዛዝ፡ ወለእመቦ፡ ብእሲ፡ ጋኔነ፡ ወአፍቀረ፡ ይባእ፡ ውስተ፡ ሕግነ፡ ይመሀርዎ፡ ፈሪሀ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ቀዲሙ፡ ወይፈውስዎ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
