<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.18.14> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 14, if the person lives an adulterous life and makes it a habit, ፲፬ ትእዛዝ፡ እመቦ፡ ብእሲ፡ ዘይነብር፡ በዝሙት፡ ወገብረ፡ ውእተ፡ ልማደ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
