	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 15, Likewise, an adulterous woman must either leave her adulterous life or be turned away, ፲፭ ትእዛዝ፡ ወከማሁ፡ ብእሲት፡ ዘማዊት፡ እመሂ፡ ትሕድግ፡ ዝሙታ፡ ወትትመየጥ፡ ወእመ፡ አኮ፡ ትሰደድ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
