	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 16, If a person makes an idol or graven image from stone, or from wood, or from metal, ፲፮ ትእዛዝ፡ እመቦ፡ ብእሲ፡ ዘይገብር፡ ጣዖተ፡ ወግልፎ፡ ዘእብን፡ አው፡ ዘዕፅ፡ አው፡ ዘብርት፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
