	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 17, If a man or a woman from another (religion) wants to enter into our faith, ፲፯ ትእዛዝ፡ እመቦ፡ ብእሲ፡ አው፡ ብእሲት፡ እምነኪር፡ ወይፈቅዱ፡ ይባኡ፡ ውስተ፡ ሕግነ፡" ;
