	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 19, If a man marries a woman among the faithful and then commits evil in his flesh, such as adultery, ትእዛዝ፡ ፲፱ እመቦ፡ ብእሲ፡ ዘአውሰበ፡ ብእሲተ፡ መሃምንተ፡ ወይገብር፡ እኩየ፡ በሥጋሁ፡ ዝሙተ፡" ;
