	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 20, If a woman is a concubine for a man who is an unbeliever, ትእዛዝ፡ ፳ እመቦ፡ ዕቅብተ፡ ለብእሲ፡ ዘኢየአምን፡" ;
