	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 23, A person among the faithful who wants to be numbered with those who do good works and who enter into solitude, ትእዛዝ፡ ፳፫ ዘይፈቅድ፡ እመሃይምናን፡ በክርስቶስ፡ ይኩን፡ ውስተ፡ ኆልቈ፡ እለ፡ ይገብሩ፡ ሠናየ፡ ወይፀመድ፡ በጽሙና፡" ;
