	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 24, If a person turns his passion to watching [secular] songs, ትእዛዝ ፳፬ እመቦ፡ ብእሲ፡ ዘይመጦ፡ ፍትወቱ፡ ውስተ፡ ነጽሮ፡ ማኅሌት፡" ;
