	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 25, If one among the faithful wants to teach people about good works, then he must be calm with his words and gracious in his life (lit. body), ትእዛዝ፡ ፳፭ እመቦ፡ ሕዝባዊ፡ ዘይሜሀር፡ ሰብአ፡ ለሠናይ፡ ጽመወ፡ በቃሉ፡ ወኄረ፡ በሥጋሁ፡" ;
