	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "This synod is the Order of the Rule of the Apostles with Clement, sent to the Gentiles for the Rule of the Church, ዝንቱ፡ ሲኖዶስ፡ ሥርዓተ፡ ሐዋርያት፡ ምስለ፡ ቀሌምንጦስ፡ ዘተፈነወ፡ ለአሕዛብ፡ ሕገ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡" ;
