<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.19.1> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 1, The bishop must be ordained on a Sunday by two or three bishops, [ትእዛዝ፡] ፩ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ይሠየም፡ እንከ፡ እምኤጲስ፡ ቆጶሳት፡ ፪ አው፡ ፫ በዕለተ፡ ሰንበት፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
_:bc1a4dee161fd75387d7b79e91249dec a <https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/Locus> ;
