<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.19.2> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 2, The priest or deacon or others must be ordained on a Sunday by a bishop, ትእዛዝ፡ ፪ ቀሲስ፡ እምአሐዱ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ወዲያቆን፡ ወባዕዳንሂ፡ ከማሁ፡ በሰንበተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
_:cdce7b8c469fd8fe896e7a436ca8da71 a <https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/Locus> ;
