<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.19.3> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 3, If a bishop or a priest offers a strange offering on the altar not in accordance with the word of God, ትእዛዝ፡ ፫ ለእመቦ፡ እንከ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ወእመሂ፡ ቀሲስ፡ ዘእንበለ፡ ዘእግዚአብሔር፡ ሥርዓተ፡ ለምሥዋዕ፡ ዘያቄርቡ፡ ባዕደ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
_:e9349fe6ab148d09f46ecc9032d6204d a <https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/Locus> ;
	<https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/locusFrom> "" .
