<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.19.4> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 4, at the permitted time it is inappropriate to bring anything to the altar except for the newly-harvested fig or wheat, ትእዛዝ፡ ፬  በጊዜ፡ ይትፈቀድ፡ ዘእንበለ፡ ሐዲስ፡ በለስ፡ ወቀምሕ፡ ኢይከውን፡ ያብኡ፡ ምንተኒ፡ ኀበ፡ ምሥዋእ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
