	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 5, Other grains in the house must be sent first to the bishop or the priest, ትእዛዝ፡ ፭ ወባዕደ፡ ኵሎ፡ አቅማኅ፡ ውስተ፡ ቤት፡ ይትፈነዉ፡ ቀዳሚ፡ ለኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ወለቀሲስ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
