	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 6, if a bishop or a priest or a deacon does [secular] business like people of the world, ትእዛዝ፡ ፮ እመሂ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ወእመሂ፡ ቀሲስ፡ ወእመሂ፡ ዲያቆን፡ ዘሰብአ፡ ዓለም፡ ትካዛተ፡ ዘይገብሩ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
