	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 9, Those who enter into the church and do not listen to the readings, ትእዛዝ፡ ፱ ኵሎሙ፡ እለ፡ ቦኡ፡ ውስተ፡ [ቤተ፡] ክርስቲያን፡ ዐቢየ፡ ወእለሂ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ኢሰምዑ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
