	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 10, If anyone prays in the house of one who is excommunicated, he also must be excommunicated, ትእዛዝ፡ ፲ እመቦ፡ ዘምስለ፡ ቅዉም፡ ወቤት፡ ይጼሊ፡ ይሠዐር፡ ውእቱኒ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
