	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 11, If anyone is excommunicated among the ordained or among the laity, and if he did not accept the excommunication and went to another city, ትእዛዝ፡ ፲፩ እመቦ፡ ሥዩም፡ ወእመሂ፡ እምሕዝብ፡ ቅውም፡ ወእመአኮ፡ ኢቅውም፡ ሐዊሮ፡ ውስተ፡ ሀገር፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
