	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 13, For a bishop it is inappropriate for him to leave his dioscese, ፲፫ ለኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ኢይከውኖ፡ ኃዲጎ፡ ዘዚአሁ፡ በሐውርት፡. Canon 12 is missing" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
