	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 15, If the bishop violates the order in front of those over which he is appointed, ትእዛዝ፡ ፲፭፡ ወእመሰ፡ [ኤጲስ፡] ቆጶስ፡ ኀበ፡ ዘሀለዉ፡ ቀሊለ፡ ረሰየ፡ እንተ፡ ላዕሌሆሙ፡ ተሠርዐ፡ ሥርዐት፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
