	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 16, If a person after his baptism married two wives or if he bought a concubine, ትእዛዝ፡ ፲፯ ዘክልኤተ፡ አውሰበ፡ እምድኅረ፡ ተጠምቀ፡ ወእመሂ፡ ዕቅብተ፡ አጥረየ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
