	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 17, If a person takes as a wife a widow or a divorced woman or a second wife or an adulteress, ትእዛዝ፡ ፲፯፡ ዘማዕስብ፡ ነሥአ፡ ወእመሂ፡ ኅድግተ፡ ወእመሂ፡ ካልእተ፡ አመተ፡ ወእመሂ፡ ዘማ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
