	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 18, If a person marries two sisters or the daughter of his sister, then he cannot be ordained, ትእዛዝ፡ ፲፰ ዘክልኤ፡ አሐተ፡ አውሰበ፡ ወእመ[፡]አኮ፡ ወለተ፡ እኅቱ፡ ኢይክል ይሠየም።" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
