	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 19, A clergyman who bribes must be demoted, ትእዛዝ፡ ፲፱ ሥዩም፡ ኀበ፡ ዘይሁብ፡ ይሠዐር፡" ;
