	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 20, A person from our faith who was forcibly castrated by the people, ትእዛዝ፡ ፳ ኅፅው፡ ለእመ፡ እምተሐየሎ፡ ሰብአ፡ ዘከማነ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
