	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 22, One from the clergy who castrated himself, ትእዛዝ፡ ፳፪ ለእመቦ፡ እንዘ፡ ሥዩም፡ ውእቱ፡ መተረ፡ ርእሶ፡" ;
