	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 34, The bishop cannot violate the jurisdiction of another diascese and ordain someone in another jurisdiction, ፴፬ ትእዛዝ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ኢይድፍር፡ ባዕደ፡ እምዘዚአሁ፡ መካናት፡ ሢመታተ፡ ኢይግበር፡" ;
