	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 37, The bishop must be conscious that the work of the church is in accordance with what is shown in the word of God, ትእዛዝ፡ ፴፯ ወኵሎ፡ ዘቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን ዘትካት፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ይርከብ፡ ሕሊና፡ ወሥራዕ፡ ሕገ፡ ዘእግዚአብሔር፡" ;
