	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 39, The church property and the [personal] property of the bishop must be distinguished, ፴፱ ትእዛዝ፡ ይኩን፡ ዕውቀ፡ ዚአሁ፡ ለኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ንዋዩ፡ቦ ወዕውቅ፡ ዘቤተ፡ ክርስቲያንሂ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
