	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 46, If a layperson leaves his wife and takes another, ፵፮ ትእዛዝ፡ እመቦ፡ ሕዝባዊ፡ ብእሲቶ፡ ኃዲጎ፡ ካልእተ፡ ነሥአ፡" ;
