	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 52, If any of the clergy mocks the deaf or the lame or the blind, he must be excommunicated, ፶፪ እመኒ፡ ሥዩመ፡ ወጽሙመ፡ ጽሉለ፡ ወሐንካሳ፡ ወዕውረ፡ ዘይሳለቅ፡ ይቁም፡" ;
