	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 55, If a person brings into the church books written by heretics, ትእዛዝ፡ ፶፭፡ እመቦ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ሐሰት፡ ዘተጽሕፈ፡ ለረሲዐን፡ መጻሕፍት፡ ከመ፡ ቅዱሳን፡ ዘቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
