	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 56, If there is a rumor among the faithful about adultery [in a person seeking admittance], ትእዛዝ፡ ፶፯፡ እመቦ፡ ሐሜተ፡ ዘኮነ፡ ዲበ፡ መሃይምናን፡ በእንተ፡ ብእሲት፡ ብእሲ፡ ወእመኒ፡ ካልአ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
