	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 58, If a bishop or a priest or a deacon eat the flesh of an animal with the blood with its life, or killed by a wild animal, ፶፰ ትእዛዝ፡ እመቦ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ወእመሂ፡ ቀሲስ፡ ወእመሂ፡ ዲያቆን፡ ወእመ፡ አኮ፡ ዘኮነ፡ እምሥዋዕ፡ ይበል፡ በደሙ፡ በነፍሱ፡  እመኒ፡ ማውታ፡ በአርዌ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
