	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 60, If anyone from the clergy or laity enters into the synagogue of the Jews, or into the abode of the heretic to pray, ፷ ትእዛዝ፡ እመኒ፡ ሥዩም፡ ወእመኒ፡ ሕዝባዊ፡ ዘቦአ፡ ምኵራበ፡ አይሁድ፡ ወእመኒ፡ ዘውስተ፡ ዕልዋን፡ ይጼሊ፡ " ;
