	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 61, If anyone from the clergy attack or assault another person to kill him, ፷፩ ትእዛዝ፡ እመቦ፡ ሥዩም፡ ቦባእሰ፡ ወቦጕድአተ፡ ወምጕዳአ፡ አሐቲ፡ ቀተለ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
