	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 62, If a person rapes a virgin who is not engaged [to him], let him be excommunicated, ትእዛዝ፡ ፷፪ እመቦ፡ ድንግለ፡ ዘኢፍሕርተ፡ ተኃይሎ፡ ነሥአ፡ ይቁም፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
