	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 64, If a bishop, or a priest, or a deacon, or a reader, or a cantor does observe the Lenten [lit. Holy Easter] fast, ትእዛዝ፡ ፷፬ እመቦ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ወቀሲስ፡ ወዲያቆን፡ ወእመኒ፡ አናጕንስጢስ፡ ወመዘምር፡ ቅድስተ፡ ጾመ፡ ፋሲካ፡ ዘኢይጸውም፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
