	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 67, If a Christian takes anointing oil to the pagan temple, ትእዛዝ፡ ፷፯፡ እመቦ፡ ክርስቲያናዊ፡ ቅብአ፡ ዘይወስድ፡ ቤተ፡ አማልክት፡" ;
