	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 69, Do not accept a heretic’s witness over the witness of a bishop or of a single layperson, ትእዛዝ፡ ፷፱ ዘኮነ፡ ስምዐ፡ ዲበ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ዕልወ፡ ኢይንሥኡ፡ አላ፡ ወኢመሃይምነ፡ አሐደ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
