	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 70, It is not appropriate for the bishop to pass his appointment to his brother or his children, or relatives, ትእዛዝ፡ ፸ እስመ፡ ኢርቱዕ፡ ለኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ለእኁሁ፡ ወለእመኒ፡ ለውሉዱ፡ ወእመአኮ፡ ለአዝማዲሁ፡ ኢይጼጉ፡ ሢመቶ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
