	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 71, A person with poor eyesight or a disabled foot [i.e., with mild disabilities] should be able to be a bishop, ትእዛዝ፡ ፸፩ እመቦ፡ ጽውሰ፡ ዐይን፡ ወፅውሰ፡ እግር፡ ይደልዎ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
