<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.19.79> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 72, A disabled or a blind person may not be a bishop not because it is unclean to be blind or disabled, but rather that the work of the work of the church be not set aside, ፸፪ ትእዛዝ፡ ጽሙም፡ ወዕውር፡ ኢይሠየም፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ አኮ፡ ርኩስ፡ ከዊኖ፡ አላ፡ ከመ፡ ግብረ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ኢይጸራዕ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
