	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 75, Slaves cannot enter into ordination without permission of their master, ፸፭ ትእዛዝ፡ አግብርት፡ ውስተ፡ ሢመት፡ ዘእንበለ፡ ፈቃደ፡ አጋእዝቲሆሙ፡ ኢናበውሕ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
