	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 76, If a bishop, or a priest, or a deacon lives with soldiers [i.e., becomes a soldier himself], ፸፮ ትእዛዝ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ወእመኒ፡ ቀሲስ፡ ወእመኒ፡ ዲያቆን፡ ምስለ፡ ሐራ፡ ዘይነብር፡" ;
