	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 15, Any person who practices astrology and believes in those who practice charms and magic is prohibited from ordination, ፲፭ ትእዛዝ፡ ወይእትት፡ እምሢመት፡ ኵሉ፡ ዘይትአመን፡ በሐሳበ፡ ከዋክብት፡ ወዘየአምን፡ ነገረ፡ ማርያን፡ ወሰብአ፡ ሥራይ፡" ;
