	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 17, Any priest or deacon who is known for his adulterous life must be deposed, ፲፯ ትእዛዝ፡ ወ[ይ]ሥዐር፡ እምሢመቱ፡ ኵሉ፡ ቀሲስ፡ ወዲያቆን፡ ዘይትዐወቅ፡ በዝሙት፡" ;
