	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 18, A person who collaborates with the Jews must not be a member of the clergy and must be prohibited from the service of the church, ፲፰ ትእዛዝ፡ ወኢየሀሉ፡ ውስተ፡ ሢመት፡ ወ[መ]ልእክተ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ወኢይደመር፡ ምስለ፡ ካህናት፡ ዘያፈቅሮሙ፡ ለአይሁድ፡" ;
