	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 5, Bishops, priests, and deacons, cannot collaborate with [i.e., be consumed by] the business of this world, ፭ ትእዛዝ፡ ወኢይደመሩ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶሳት፡ ቀሳውስት፡ ወዲያቆናት፡ ውስተ፡ ግብረ፡ ዝንቱ፡ ዓለም፡" ;
