	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 8, Let the person who prays in his house and does not participate at the church be excommunicated, ትእዛዝ፡ ፰ ወለመ፡ ቦ፡ ዘጸለየ፡ ምስለ፡ ዘኢይሳተፍ፡ ምሥጢር፡ ለእመ፡ በቤት፡ ይሰደድ፡" ;
