	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 46, On the person who does not fast for Lent, or on Wednesday or on Friday, ፵፮ ትእዛዝ፡ በእንተ፡ ዘኢይጸውም፡ ጾመ፡ አርብዐ፡ ረቡዐ፡ ወዐርበ፡" ;
