	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Canon 48, On a person who steals oil or candle from the church, ፵፰ ትእዛዝ፡ በእንተ፤ ዘይሠርቅ፡ ቅብአ፡ እው፡ ማኅቶተ፡. There is no canon 49" ;
