	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 2, If they bring a person to be appointed as a bishop, it must be by the approval of the people of his province, አብጢሊስ፡ ፪ እመቦ፡ ብእሲ፡ ዘአምጽእዎ፡ ከመ፡ ይሠየም፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ወይኩን፡ ዝንቱ፡ በስምረተ፡ ሰብአ፡ ብሔሮሙ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
