	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 3, If a bishop, or a priest, or a deacon disregards the law of Christ in communion and brings honey or milk, etc., to the altar, አብጢሊስ፡ ፫ እመሂ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ አው፡ ቀሲስ፡ አው፡ ዲያቆን፡ ዘተዐደወ፡ ሕገ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ በውስተ፡ ቁርባን፡ ወአቅረበ፡ ላዕለ፡ ምሥዋዕ፡ መዐረ፡ አው፡ ሐሊበ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
