	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 4, On those who bring the first of their fruits or the firstborn of their animals for the sake of their soul, አብጥሊስ፡ ፬ ኵሉ፡ ዘብፅዑ፡ መሃይምናን፡ በእንተ፡ ነፍሶሙ፡ ቀዳሜ፡ ፍሬሆያቲሆሙ፡ ወበኵረ፡ እንስሳሆሙ፡" ;
