<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.6> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 5, If a bishop, or a priest, or a deacon sends his wife from his house because of the ascetic life,  አብጥሊስ፡ ፭ እመሂ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ አው፡ ቀሲስ፡ አው፡ ዲያቆን፡ ዘያወፅእ፡ ብእሲቶ፡ እማኅደሩ፡ በምክንያተ፡ ጽሙና፡" ;
