	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 6, On how it is inappropriate for bishops, priests, and deacons who are compensated by the church to be involved in the business of this world, አብጥሊስ፡ ፮ እስመ፡ ኢይደልዎሙ፡ ለኤጲስ፡ ቆጶሳት፡ ለቀሳውስት፡ ወለዲያቆናት፡ እለ፡ ትኩላን፡ ለቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ እምተግባረ፡ ዓለም፡" ;
