<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.21> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 20, If a person is forcibly castrated, አብጥሊስ፡ ፳ እመቦ፡ ብእሲ፡ ኅፅው፡ ዘኃፀውዎ፡ ወእመሂ፡ ተኃየልዎ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
_:d1fe5529a8c233e6ee02f54d66c878ae a <https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/Locus> ;
	<https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/locusFrom> "" .
<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.21> <https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/hasLocus> _:d1fe5529a8c233e6ee02f54d66c878ae .
<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.22> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 21, If a person castrates himself willingly, አብጥሊስ፡ ፳፩ እመቦ፡ ብእሲ፡ ዘኃጸወ፡ ርእሶ፡ በፈቃዱ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
_:e09ed84b16f672ff8366e9d571240e10 a <https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/Locus> ;
