<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.23> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 22, If a person castrates himself after he is ordained, አብጥሊስ፡ ፳፪ እመቦ፡ ብእሲ፡ ዘኃፀወ፡ ርእሶ፡ ሐዲስ፡ እምድኅረ፡ ክህነት፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
_:e87f0c7c7c408d214cbffe5ec79c879d a <https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/Locus> ;
	<https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/locusFrom> "" .
<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.23> <https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/hasLocus> _:e87f0c7c7c408d214cbffe5ec79c879d .
<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.24> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 23, If a person castrates himself after his conversion, አብጥሊስ፡፳፫ እመቦ፡ አምነ፡ ዘኃፀወ፡ ርእሶ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
