	<https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/locusFrom> "" .
<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.24> <https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/hasLocus> _:c3f3ad34fba9f42f81877879f0e28169 .
<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.25> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 24, If a bishop, a priest, a deacon, or others lower in their appointment are found in adultery or swear falsely, አብጥሊስ፡ ፳፬ እመሂ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ አው፡ ቀሲስ፡ አው፡ ዲያቆን፡ አው፡ ዘይቴሐቶሙ፡ እመዐርገ፡ ክህነቶሙ፡ ዘተረክበ፡ በዝሙት፡ አው፡ መሐለ፡ በሐሰት፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
