<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.27> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> " Decree 25,If a person enters the church and receives ordination, we instruct him to marry, if he desires, አብጥሊስ፡ ፳፭ እመቦ፡ ብእሲ፡ ዘቦአ፡ ውስተ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ወተወክፈ፡ ክህነት፡ እምጽድቅ፡ ንኅነ፡ ንኤዝዝ፡ ከመ፡ ያውስብ፡ ለእመ፡ ፈተወ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
_:e29181273b2bd9e5ecb38edd4bf72cc a <https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/Locus> ;
