<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.28> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 26, If a bishop, or a priest, or a deacon attacks the faithful, አብጥሊስ፡ ፳፮ እመሂ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ አው፡ ቀሲስ፡ አው፡ ዲያቆን፡ ለእመ፡ ዘበጠ፡ መሃይምነ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
_:d9e3dfea3bf3fea22ab3ffcd0ef6a9e2 a <https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/Locus> ;
	<https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/locusFrom> "" .
<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.28> <https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/hasLocus> _:d9e3dfea3bf3fea22ab3ffcd0ef6a9e2 .
<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.29> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 27, If a bishop, or a priest, or a deacon is excommunicated for sins he committed, አብጥሊስ፡ ፳፯ እመሂ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ አው፡ ቀሲስ፡ አው፡ ዲያቆን፡ ዘአውጽእዎ፡ እምቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ በእንተ፡ አበሳ፡ ዘገብረ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
_:a86fd28e5e7b342c3c5ca740ad91c608 a <https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/Locus> ;
