<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.29> <https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/hasLocus> _:a86fd28e5e7b342c3c5ca740ad91c608 .
<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.31> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 28, If a bishop, or a priest, or a deacon profits in any way from holy ordination, አብጥሊስ፡ ፳፰ እመሂ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ አው፡ ቀሲስ፡ አው፡ ዲያቆን፡ ዘአጥረዩ፡ ወኢምንተኒ፡ እመዐርገ፡ ክህነት፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
_:c40e3f3745ba68c9c3075395c775a5b7 a <https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/Locus> ;
