<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.32> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 29, If a bishop asks help of outsiders or rulers or from those appointed in this world in order to gain appointment in the church, አብጥሊስ፡ ፳፱ እመቦ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ዘተማኅፀነ፡ በእንተ፡ ሢመቱ፡ በሰብአ፡ አፍአ፡ ወበመኳንንት፡ ወሥዩማነ፡ ዝንቱ፡ ዓለም፡ ከመ፡ ይርድእዎ፡ ላዕለ፡ ሢመተ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
