<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.35> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 32, A bishop cannot receive any priest or deacon who come from distant provinces [without examining them, etc.], አብጥሊስ፡ ፴፪ ወኢይትወከፉ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ መነሂ፡ እምቀሳውስት፡ ወእምዲያቆናት፡ እንግዳ፡ እለ፡ መጽኡ፡ እምበሐውርት፡ ርሑቅ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
