<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.36> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 33, It is appropriate for a bishop to know his appropriate duties, አብጥሊስ፡ ፴፫ ወይደልዎ፡ ለኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ከመ፡ ያእምር፡ ዘይደልዎ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
