<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.43> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 34, It is inappropriate for a bishop to ordain through bribary, አብጥሊስ፡ ፴፬ ኢመፍትው፡ ለኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ይሢም፡ በሕልያን፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
_:bdfe696e71bea55874b83ade092a30e8 a <https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/Locus> ;
	<https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/locusFrom> "" .
