<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.44> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 35, If a person is appointed as a bishop and does not execute his duties properly, አብጥሊስ፡ ፴፭ እመቦ፡ ብእሲ፡ ዘተሰይመ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ወኢቆመ፡ በርቱዕ፡ ለኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስና፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
