<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.45> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 36, We instruct the assembly to convene twice a year, አብጥሊስ፡ ፴፮ እዘዝነ፡ ከመ፡ ይኩን፡ ጉባኤ፡ ይትጋብኡ፡ በበ፡ ዐመት፡ ፪ግዜ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
