<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.46> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 37, All the property of the church must be under the control (lit. at the hand) of the bishop, አብጥሊስ፡ ፴፮ ኵሉ፡ ንዋየ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ወኵሉ፡ ዘዚአሃ፡ ይኵን፡ ውስተ እዴሁ፡ ለኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
