<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.48> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 39, The property of a bishop must be separated from the property of the church, አብጥሊስ፡ ፴፱ ለይኩን፡ ንዋየ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ በባሕቲቱ፡ እምንዋየ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡" ;
