	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 40, We instruct that a bishop must exercise great care with the property of the church, አብጥሊስ፡ ፵ ንኤዝዝ፡ ይኩን፡ ስሉጠ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ላዕለ፡ ንዋየ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
