	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 41, If a bishop or a priest, or a deacon desires interest for what he lends, አብጥሊስ፡ ፵፩ እመቦ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ አው፡ ቀሲስ፡ አው፡ ዲያቆን፡ ዘኃሠሠ፡ እምኀበ፡ ዘለቅሐ፡ ረድኤተ፡ አው፡ ርዴ፡. There is no decree 42" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
