<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.54> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 45, Likewise, if the faithful leave [marriage] for the sake of the ascetic life, and if a bishop, a priest, or a deacon does not receive the repentance of a person who commits sin, አብጥሊስ፡ ፵፭ ወከማሁ፡ መሃይምናን፡ ወካዕበ፡ ዘኃደገ፡ ዘንተ፡ ኵሎ፡ በእንተ፡ አምልኮ፡ ወጽሙና፡ እመቦ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ አው፡ ቀሲስ፡ አው፡ ዲያቆን፡ ዘኢተወክፈ፡ ንስሐሁ፡ ለኃጥእ፡ ለእመ፡ አበሰ፡ ወነስሐ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
_:ca26949b4829b04a01acabc8744462d7 a <https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/Locus> ;
	<https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/locusFrom> "" .
