<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.55> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 46, If a bishop, or a priest, or a deacon does not eat meat or drink wine on the feast days, አብጥሊስ፡ ፵፮ እመሂ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ አው፡ ቀሲስ፡ አው፡ ዲያቆን፡ ዘኢበልዐ፡ ሥጋ፡ ወኢሰትየ፡ ወይን፡ በመዋዕለ፡ በዐላት፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
