<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.56> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 47, If a clergyman eats a meal inside a tavern, አብጥሊስ፡ ፵፯ እመቦ፡ ብእሲ፡ እምካህናት፡ ዘበልዐ፡ መባልዕተ፡ በውስተ፡ ምዝፋናት፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
