<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.57> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 48, If a clergyman curses a bishop or expresses his spite or hatred to outsiders, አብጥሊስ፡ ፵፰ እመቦ፡ ካህን፡ ዘረገመ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ አው፡ መንኖ፡ ወጸአሎ፡ በከ፡ ነገረ፡ ሰብአ፡ አፍአ፡." ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
_:fee2779cbff3a5eef0d91f15891c9f5b a <https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/Locus> ;
