<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.58> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 49, If a layperson hates a priest or a deacon, አብጥሊስ፡ ፵፱ እመቦ፡ ብእሲ፡ እምካህናት፡ መሃይምናን፡ ዘፀአለ፡ ቀሲስ፡ አው፡ ዲያቆነ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
_:d66a9a75a93788166c180413c2689ba6 a <https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/Locus> ;
