<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.58> <https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/hasLocus> _:d66a9a75a93788166c180413c2689ba6 .
<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.59> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 50, If a clergyman or a layman mocks or laughs at the deaf, blind, or the mute, or the lame, etc., አብጥሊስ፡ ፶ እመቦ፡ ብእሲ፡ እምካህናት፡ አው፡ ሕዝባውያን፡ ዘተሳለቀ፡ እው ሰሐቀ፡ ብእሴ፡ ጽሙመ፡ እው፡ ዕውረ፡፡ አው፡ በሃመ፤ አው፡ ሐንካሳ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
_:d6a9b279fd5a8305cccf052b5ce94bcf a <https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/Locus> ;
