<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.60> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 51, If a man, woman, or layperson hates a priest or a deacon and curses them, አብጥሊስ፡ ፶፩ እመቦ፡ ብእሲ፡ ወብእሲት፡ አው፡ መሃይምን፡ ዘፀአለ፡ ቀሲሰ፡ አው፡ ዲያቆነ፡ ወረገሞ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
_:b7dfb88c5c970012e690df17aecae990 a <https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/Locus> ;
