<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.64> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 55, If a layperson falls into adultery and makes it a daily practice, ፶፭ እመቦ፡ ብእሲ፡ መሃይምን፡ ዘወድቀ፡ በአብዝኆ፡ ዝሙት፡ ወኮነ፡ ውእቱ፡ ልማደ፡ ዘወትር፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
