<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.65> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 57, If a clergyman or a layman denies his faith for fear of the Jews, pagans, or heretics, አብጥሊስ፡ ፶፯ እመቦ፡ ብእሲ፡ እምካህናት፡ አው፡ እምሕዝባዊያን፡ ዘክሕደ፡ ሃይማኖቶ፡ እምፍርሀተ፡ አይሁድ፡ ወአረሚ፡ ወዕልዋን፡ " ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
