<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.67> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 59, If a clergyman or a layman fasts on the Sabbath or on the Great Sunday which is Easter, አብጥሊስ፡ ፶፱ እመቦ፡ ብእሲ፡ እምካህናት፡ ወእምሕዝባዊያን፡ ዘገብረ፡ ጾመ፡ በዕለተ፡ ሰንበት፡ ወእኁድ፡ ዐቢይ፡ ዝ፡ ውእቱ፡ ፋሲካ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
_:bf7f11c9b8803fbb200119e7b14af246 a <https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/Locus> ;
	<https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/locusFrom> "" .
