<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.68> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 60, If a priest or a layman enters the synagogue of the Jews or into the house of heretics for prayer, አብጥሊስ፡ ፷ እመቦ፡ ካህን፡ እው፡ ሕዝባዊ፡ መሃይምን፡ ቦአ፡ ምኵራበ፡ አይሁድ፡ ለጸሎት፡ ወቤተ፡ ዕልዋን፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
_:facec74d59f83e9d20c6785d93584546 a <https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/Locus> ;
