<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.69> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 61, If a clergyman fights with another person and attacks him and if the person dies, አብጥሊስ፡ ፷፩ እመቦ፡ ብእሲ፡ እምካህናት፡ ዘተቃረነ፡ ምስለ፡ ካልእ፡ ብእሲ፡ ወዘበጠ፡ ወሞተ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
