<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.72> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 64, If a clergyman is ordained twice, ፷፬ አብጥሊስ፡ እመቦ፡ ካህን፡ ዘተሠይመ፡ ዳግመ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
