<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.73> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 65, If a clergyman does not fast the great fast (i.e., Lent), አብጥሊስ፡ ፷፭ እመቦ፡ ብእሲ፡ እምካህናት፡ ዘኢይጸውም፡ ዐቢየ፡ ጾመ፡" ;
