<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.74> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 66, If a clergyman or a layman fasts with the Jews in their fasting, አብጥሊስ፡ ፷፮ አመቦ፡ ብእሲ፡ እምካህናት፡ ወእምሕዝባዊያን፡ ዘይጸውም፡ ምስለ፡ አይሁድ፡ በጾሞሙ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
_:ca693a841407484c8b4585c53c90f6ac a <https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/Locus> ;
