<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.75> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 67, If a clergyman or a layman sends offerings to the synagogue of the Jews, አብጥሊስ፡ ፷፯ እመቦ፡ ብእሲ፡ እምካህናት፡ አው፡ እምሕዝባዊያን፡ ዘይፌኑ፡ ለምኵራበ፡ አይሁድ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
_:ad19a110bbafba2a120a7b4182384dce a <https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/Locus> ;
