<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.76> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 68, If a clergyman or a layman steals from the church oil, candle, etc., አብጥሊስ፡ ፷፰ እመቦ፡ ካህን፡ አው፡ ሕዝባዊ፡ ዘይሠርቅ፡ እምቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ቅብአ፡ አው፡ ስምዕ፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
_:e67627119446bac30b461bc3314e78db a <https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/Locus> ;
	<https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/locusFrom> "" .
