<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.78> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 70, If clergymen or laymen accuse a bishop and if there is no judge [above the bishop] in the province, አብጥሊስ፡ ፸ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ለእለ፡ ሰከይዎ፡ ካህናት፡ ሥዩማን፡ መሃይምናን፡ ወለእመ፡ አልቦሙ፡ በውእቱ፡ ብሔር፡ መኰንነ፡." ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
