	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 71, They do not have to receive the testimony of two young men (? ክልኤቱ፡ ዕደው፡) over the witness of a bishop or the witness of one layperson, አብጥሊስ፡ ፸፩ ስምዐ፡ ክልኤቱ፡ ዕደው፡ ላዕለ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ወኢስምዐ፡ አሐዱ፡ መሃይምን፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
