<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.82> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 74, It is not appropriate for a bishop to appoint the [totally] blind, the deaf, the mute, etc., አብጥሊስ፡ ፸፬ ኢይደልዎ፡ ይሠየም፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ዕውር፡ አው፡ ጽሙም፡ አው፡ በሃም፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
