<https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP01921/msitem/ms_i1.23.83> a <https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem> , <https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont> ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "Decree 75, A person with epilepsy or possessed by a demon may not be appointed, አብጥሊስ፡ ፸፭ እመቦ፡ ብእሲ፡ ዘነገርጋር፡ አው፡ እው፡ ዘጋንኔ፡ ኢይሠየም፡" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
